MARIJUANA IS SPREADING RAPIDLY--

09:39.946 --> 09:41.014
NOWHERE MORE SO THAN IN

09:41.014 --> 09:42.949
COLORADO, WHERE THE LEGAL SALE

09:42.949 --> 09:44.350
OF MARIJUANA FOR RECREATIONAL

09:44.350 --> 09:45.985
USE IS BEGINNING ITS SECOND

09:45.985 --> 09:46.853
YEAR.

