THAT PUT HIM IN POSITION TO BE

10:36.469 --> 10:37.837
ONE OF THE FIRST TO SELL

10:37.837 --> 10:39.506
RECREATIONAL CANNABIS WHEN IT

10:39.506 --> 10:41.574
BECAME LEGAL LAST YEAR.

10:41.574 --> 10:43.543
BUSINESS HAS BEEN SO GOOD THAT

10:43.543 --> 10:46.112
WILLIAMS NOW EMPLOYS 75 PEOPLE

10:46.112 --> 10:48.114
AND EXPECTS TO HIRE MORE.

10:48.114 --> 10:49.716
AND THIS PAST AUGUST HE OPENED A

10:49.716 --> 10:51.584
NEW STATE-OF-THE ART FACILITY

10:51.584 --> 10:53.887
THAT WILL PRODUCE 7,000 POUNDS

10:53.887 --> 10:55.622
OF CANNABIS A YEAR.

10:55.622 --> 10:56.823
>> IT'S MANUFACTURING IS WHAT IT

10:56.823 --> 10:59.359
IS, AS FAR AS I'M CONCERNED.

10:59.359 --> 11:01.628
YOU ARE MANUFACTURING MARIJUANA.

11:01.628 --> 11:03.229
THIS IS AN INDUSTRIAL

11:03.229 --> 11:06.165
MANUFACTURING PLANT THAT GROWS

11:06.165 --> 11:07.100
MARIJUANA.

11:07.100 --> 11:08.234
>> Reporter: STORES LIKE THESE

11:08.234 --> 11:09.869
CAN NOW SELL UP TO AN OUNCE OF

11:09.869 --> 11:11.437
MARIJUANA TO CUSTOMERS WHO ARE

11:11.437 --> 11:12.805
21 AND OVER.

