THE PRODUCTS COME IN ALL KINDS

11:14.574 --> 11:17.443
OF FORMS: CANNABIS BUDS FROM A

11:17.443 --> 11:19.345
RANGE OF VARIETIES BRED TO TREAT

11:19.345 --> 11:21.481
PARTICULAR AILMENTS, PROVIDE A

11:21.481 --> 11:22.715
MELLOW BUZZ, OR DELIVER A

11:22.715 --> 11:23.983
POWERFUL RUSH.

11:23.983 --> 11:26.219
PRE-ROLLED JOINTS, POT-LACED

11:26.219 --> 11:27.754
BROWNIES, HARD CANDY, AND

11:27.754 --> 11:29.622
CHOCOLATE BARS, MARIJUANA

11:29.622 --> 11:31.324
INFUSED BEVERAGES AND MASSAGE

11:31.324 --> 11:32.158
OIL.

11:32.158 --> 11:34.027
CONSUMERS SPEND TENS OF MILLIONS

11:34.027 --> 11:35.528
OF DOLLARS A MONTH ON THOSE

11:35.528 --> 11:37.297
PRODUCTS, BUT WILLIAMS IS SURE

11:37.297 --> 11:38.898
THERE'S A LOT MORE MONEY TO BE

11:38.898 --> 11:40.433
MADE IN HIS BUSINESS.

11:40.433 --> 11:42.669
>> YOU KNOW, I DID THIS SO THAT

11:42.669 --> 11:44.404
MY FAMILY CAN BE SET UP FOR

11:44.404 --> 11:45.471
THE REST OF THEIR LIVES.

11:45.471 --> 11:47.473
RIGHT NOW, I ALREADY KNOW OF

11:47.473 --> 11:49.709
SOME BLUE CHIP COMPANIES THAT

11:49.709 --> 11:51.177
ARE ON THE... ON THE START LINE.

11:51.177 --> 11:52.211
THEY'RE GOING TO COME AND BUY

11:52.211 --> 11:54.380
PEOPLE UP, AND QUITE HONESTLY, I

11:54.380 --> 11:55.615
WANT TO BE ONE OF THOSE GUYS.

11:55.615 --> 11:56.449
>> Reporter: ONE OF THE BENEFITS

11:56.449 --> 11:57.850
ATTACHED TO LEGALIZATION WAS

11:57.850 --> 11:59.085
THAT IT WOULD ELIMINATE THE

11:59.085 --> 12:00.386
BLACK MARKET.

