BUT THAT MARKET IS STILL

12:01.754 --> 12:03.456
THRIVING, ACCORDING TO A 39-

12:03.456 --> 12:05.258
YEAR-OLD MARIJUANA GROWER WHO

12:05.258 --> 12:06.993
ASKED US TO CALL HIM JOHN DOE

12:06.993 --> 12:08.428
AND CONCEAL HIS IDENTITY

12:08.428 --> 12:09.662
BECAUSE HE SELLS ON THE

12:09.662 --> 12:11.397
UNDERGROUND MARKET.

12:11.397 --> 12:12.665
THE ILLEGAL TRADE IS DOING

12:12.665 --> 12:14.300
ESPECIALLY WELL IN BLACK AND

12:14.300 --> 12:16.269
LATINO COMMUNITIES, AND HE SAYS

12:16.269 --> 12:18.071
IT WORKS THE SAME WAY IT DID

12:18.071 --> 12:19.872
WHEN POT WAS ILLEGAL.

12:19.872 --> 12:21.274
>> YOU HAVE THAT ONE GUY, THAT

12:21.274 --> 12:22.976
GUY THAT SHINES, THAT'S THE

12:22.976 --> 12:24.544
ROBIN HOOD OF THE NEIGHBORHOOD.

12:24.544 --> 12:25.645
THIS MAN SUPPLIES A LITTLE

12:25.645 --> 12:27.113
GHETTO AREA.

12:27.113 --> 12:28.081
SIMPLE AS THAT.

12:28.081 --> 12:29.282
BREAKS HIS OWN POUND INTO LITTLE

12:29.282 --> 12:31.517
OUNCES AND HELPS EVERYBODY IN

12:31.517 --> 12:32.552
HIS COMMUNITY.

12:32.552 --> 12:33.820
SO THEY CAN AFFORD IT WITH HIM.

12:33.820 --> 12:35.254
THAT'S HOW IT'S HAPPENED.

12:35.254 --> 12:36.422
>> Reporter: YEAH.

12:36.422 --> 12:38.157
AND THAT'S HOW IT HAPPENED

12:38.157 --> 12:39.225
BEFORE, TOO.

12:39.225 --> 12:39.859
>> YEAH.

12:39.859 --> 12:40.827
YEAH.

12:40.827 --> 12:41.494
NOTHING'S CHANGED.

12:41.494 --> 12:42.428
>> Reporter: JOHN DOE SAYS LOW-

12:42.428 --> 12:43.963
INCOME BUYERS TURN TO THE BLACK

12:43.963 --> 12:45.832
MARKET BECAUSE PRICES ARE HIGHER

12:45.832 --> 12:47.767
AT LEGAL RETAIL STORES.

12:47.767 --> 12:49.636
THERE'S CONFLICTING INFORMATION,

12:49.636 --> 12:50.937
BUT AN OUNCE OF POT ON THE BLACK

12:50.937 --> 12:52.305
MARKET CAN COST AS LITTLE AS

12:52.305 --> 12:54.073
$180.

12:54.073 --> 12:55.608
AT THE STORE ANDY WILLIAMS OWNS,

12:55.608 --> 12:58.411
YOU HAVE TO PAY AROUND $240 FOR

12:58.411 --> 12:59.412
AN OUNCE.

