THAT'S PARTLY BECAUSE THE PRICE

13:01.047 --> 13:04.584
INCLUDES A 15% EXCISE TAX, A 10%

13:04.584 --> 13:06.686
MARIJUANA TAX, THE STATE SALES

13:06.686 --> 13:08.655
TAX, AND DENVER'S MARIJUANA

13:08.655 --> 13:09.889
SALES TAX.

13:09.889 --> 13:11.591
>> THE TAXES ARE AN OVERREACH

13:11.591 --> 13:13.026
AND EXCESSIVE.

13:13.026 --> 13:14.927
AND IT'S A REGRESSIVE TAX AND IT

13:14.927 --> 13:16.262
IMPACTS THE POOR THE MOST.

13:16.262 --> 13:17.430
>> Reporter: LARISA BOLIVAR WAS

13:17.430 --> 13:18.564
INVOLVED IN THE FIGHT TO MAKE

13:18.564 --> 13:20.199
MARIJUANA LEGAL FOR MEDICAL

13:20.199 --> 13:21.234
PURPOSES.

13:21.234 --> 13:22.769
SHE USES IT HERSELF TO TREAT

13:22.769 --> 13:23.970
STRESS.

