SHE CAMPAIGNED FOR LEGALIZATION,

13:25.705 --> 13:27.140
BUT SHE DOESN'T LIKE HOW IT'S

13:27.140 --> 13:28.174
WORKING OUT.

13:28.174 --> 13:29.776
SHE BELIEVES ALL THOSE TAXES

13:29.776 --> 13:31.844
GUARANTEE A BLACK MARKET.

