BUT TAXES HAVE BEEN BENEFICIAL,

13:33.980 --> 13:35.815
ACCORDING TO MASON TVERT, WHO

13:35.815 --> 13:37.550
ALSO CAMPAIGNED FOR LEGALIZATION

13:37.550 --> 13:39.419
AND HELPED DRAFT THE STATE'S

13:39.419 --> 13:40.753
REGULATIONS.

13:40.753 --> 13:42.388
IN THE FIRST TEN MONTHS, THOSE

13:42.388 --> 13:44.424
TAXES HAVE GENERATED NEARLY $41

13:44.424 --> 13:46.059
MILLION.

13:46.059 --> 13:47.627
A CHUNK OF THAT IS SLATED FOR

13:47.627 --> 13:49.829
PUBLIC SCHOOL CONSTRUCTION.

13:49.829 --> 13:51.330
BESIDES, HE SAYS, THE LEGAL

13:51.330 --> 13:53.032
MARKET OFFERS SOME THINGS THAT

13:53.032 --> 13:54.834
CONSUMERS FIND MORE IMPORTANT

13:54.834 --> 13:56.436
THAN THE LOWEST PRICE.

13:56.436 --> 13:58.538
>> VARIETY, CONVENIENCE, SAFETY.

13:58.538 --> 14:00.640
THAT'S WHAT DRIVES EVERY PRODUCT

14:00.640 --> 14:02.875
IN THE ENTIRE WORLD.

14:02.875 --> 14:03.910
YOU KNOW, THAT'S WHAT'S GOING TO

14:03.910 --> 14:05.111
DRIVE THIS MARKET.

14:05.111 --> 14:08.014
IF SOMEONE IS LOWER INCOME OR A

14:08.014 --> 14:09.882
HIGHER INCOME, CHANCES ARE

14:09.882 --> 14:12.151
THEY'RE GOING TO GO TO A STORE

14:12.151 --> 14:14.087
AND PURCHASE IT BECAUSE IT'LL BE

14:14.087 --> 14:15.054
SAFE.

14:15.054 --> 14:16.589
IT'LL BE CONVENIENT.

14:16.589 --> 14:17.657
THERE'LL BE VARIETY.

14:17.657 --> 14:18.825
THESE ARE WHAT DRIVE PEOPLE'S

14:18.825 --> 14:19.726
DECISIONS.

14:19.726 --> 14:20.993
>> Reporter: HOW HAS THAT WORKED

14:20.993 --> 14:21.828
OUT SO FAR?

14:21.828 --> 14:22.562
I MEAN, IS THE BLACK MARKET

14:22.562 --> 14:23.429
GONE?

14:23.429 --> 14:25.798
IS THE BLACK MARKET GOING AWAY?

14:25.798 --> 14:26.566
>> I THINK IT'S ABSURD FOR

14:26.566 --> 14:27.633
ANYONE TO ASSUME THAT WE CAN

14:27.633 --> 14:29.669
ELIMINATE A BLACK MARKET THAT

14:29.669 --> 14:32.138
GREW OVER 80-PLUS YEARS WITHIN

14:32.138 --> 14:33.706
THE COURSE OF EIGHT, NINE

14:33.706 --> 14:34.574
MONTHS.

14:34.574 --> 14:36.442
BUT WE'VE SEEN THIS INDUSTRY

14:36.442 --> 14:37.543
TAKE A HUGE BITE OUT OF THE

14:37.543 --> 14:39.879
UNDERGROUND MARKET.

14:39.879 --> 14:40.813
>> Reporter: TO ENTER THE LEGAL

14:40.813 --> 14:42.315
MARIJUANA INDUSTRY, YOU HAVE TO

