>> THIS IS A SYMPTOM OF RACE

15:31.330 --> 15:35.535
RELATIONS AND ECONOMIC JUSTICE

15:35.535 --> 15:36.803
IN OUR NATION.

15:36.803 --> 15:37.770
THIS IS NOT EXCLUSIVE TO

15:37.770 --> 15:39.138
MARIJUANA.

15:39.138 --> 15:41.607
YOU KNOW, RIGHT NOW, PEOPLE IN

15:41.607 --> 15:43.142
LOWER INCOME AREAS OR

